            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;@R.. This answer is really old, but I&apos;d probably prefer a function to a macro in this case.&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/4367864/pc-luddite&quot; title=&quot;5,761 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;PC Luddite&lt;/a&gt;
